snippet.title: PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark GAME TRAILER
snippet.description:
The darkness is calling... Are you ready to face it?

Discover the world of PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark, where light is your only ally and the shadows are alive. Watch the official trailer and get a glimpse of the thrilling gameplay, unique mechanics, and the haunting atmosphere that awaits you.

Try the demo now on Steam and embark on a journey filled with mystery, danger, and unforgettable moments.

store.steampowered.com/app/2919230
